title: Beyond the Horror: Cult Episode 8
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Although I enjoyed last week’s episode, when Sarah was back this episode I actually cried because I missed her so much last week. AHS WOULD BE NOTHING WITHOUT HER.
The most disturbing for me was Kai trying to impregnate Winter in a threesome! But that song was hilarious 😂

Yes Mary! We love your prediction videos!
I want to know what Ally fed Kai, I hope the ~manwich~ had actual man in it, I know I’m twisted already but being depressed so my mind is in the dark zone. 
My insane Candyman theory is looking a little less crazy now... 🎶🐝🍯🍌
Winter killing the detective was the best!
description:
VIDEO CONTAINS SPOILERS FOR American Horror Story, Season 7, Episode 8!!!

Beyond the Horror: Cult, is an unofficial American Horror Story Live After Show. Hosted by MaryGirl Moody. Special Guests include: Casey Soper, Maisie Andrews, Jonas Bendor and Tami Sifford. We discuss and review each episode of American Horror Story Cult.
